{
  "stem": "21626.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I so missed my family that when we married, I made our home the sort of core of their existence, because they were scattered all over the place, you know.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was very fond of them all.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I still am, so-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] but I actually worked for Scotland Yard for two years afterwards.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because they found out, through their spies, that I was supposed to be working for the Czech government.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They came to interview me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was the head of the section for foreigners.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we hit it off, and he said, would you work for us?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because you seem-- you seem the right sort.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I did do that for about a year.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "What sort of work did you do?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Interviewing people and finding their political backgrounds, mainly-- sort of unobtrusively.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was a challenge.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we needed the money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was good.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I did enjoy it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, he wanted me to be his secretary after, you know, a full-time job and travel with him.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It would have been great but by then Clive was born.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I wasn't going to leave my child to these sort of nannies or anything like that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I didn't want to disrupt my own home life.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was very happy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I sort of felt-- I had lost so much in Czechoslovakia, I felt I must put my past behind me, you know, even the Jewish side of it, and just concentrate on being a typical British housewife and mother.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I tried very hard.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it wasn't till many years later I realized what a pretence I led.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It wasn't till 1968.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My sister married an English doctor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- but 40 years ago, she emigrated to New Zealand.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
